item.title: CVE-2015-1341|2024-08-06T04:40:18.678Z -- ubuntu -- apport
item.description: Any Python module in sys.path can be imported if the command line of the process triggering the coredump is Python and the first argument is -m in Apport before 2.19.2 function _python_module_path.
